      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Step into luxury with this absolutely stunning vehicle that remains in pristine, mint condition! It looks and drives exactly like it did the day it was first driven off the lot, with a flawless exterior and an interior that still feels brand new. This is a rare find for a buyer who demands perfection and a car that has been meticulously cared for every step of the way.",
