    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and offers dependable transportation for a buyer who prioritizes function over aesthetics. The exterior has several noticeable blemishes, including minor dings, some paint fading on the hood, and a few scuffs on the bumpers. Inside, the upholstery shows visible wear and some staining from regular use, though all major components remain intact. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but it will likely require some routine maintenance, such as new tires and a brake service, in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that has served us well and still has plenty of life left for its next owner.",
