      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Roll up your sleeves and get ready for a rewarding project! This vehicle is looking for a dedicated owner to restore it to its former glory. While it currently needs significant mechanical work and body repairs, it serves as a fantastic donor car or a blank canvas for someone who loves a true automotive challenge. Grab this opportunity to bring a classic back to life at a great value!",
