    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of care that borders on the fastidious. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paint, exhibits zero signs of wear or degradation. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision of a new factory unit. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a truly impeccable machine.",
